Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.50,0:00:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡……就是你們這趟旅程的終點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.70,0:00:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問……妳到底是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.70,0:00:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終點?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.00,0:00:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.40,0:00:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到我的城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:00:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜…還有克勞德…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.20,0:01:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你們兩個能夠走到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.30,0:01:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了對你們的勇氣和努力表示敬意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.90,0:01:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就陪你們玩一玩好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.80,0:01:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.90,0:01:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在什麼地方?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.10,0:01:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
