Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.10,0:01:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.50,0:01:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说……密罗奇尼亚行星也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.10,0:01:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说对了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.10,0:01:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里就是被我们毁灭的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.70,0:01:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用的也是魔石索沙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.10,0:01:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我顺便告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.70,0:01:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实魔石索沙是将行星上的生命能量吸收之后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.60,0:01:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再将它传送到异次元空间的系统
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.40,0:01:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么要做这种事?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你问我为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.70,0:02:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就是靠这种方式赖以维生的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.10,0:02:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将其它星球的生命能量…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.30,0:02:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都将成为我们活动所需的能源
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.70,0:02:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去如此，今后也是如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.60,0:02:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫做卡布力尔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.30,0:02:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是魔石索沙的魂魄……
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.50,0:02:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酸雨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.90,0:02:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.40,0:03:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们为了自己的生存
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.30,0:03:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然不惜毁灭别的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.40,0:03:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种行为根本就是天理不容
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.20,0:03:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼!你这句话倒挺像是救世主会说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救世主?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.90,0:03:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来到现在你们还不知道你们自己扮演了什么角色?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.40,0:03:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.20,0:03:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就告诉你们当作是饯别吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.50,0:03:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.00,0:03:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是尼德行星的子民
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.80,0:03:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别派遣到这个星球的巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.50,0:03:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为的就是要找寻这个与我交手的救世主
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:03:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜是个巫女?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.90,0:04:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上她也算达成这份艰难的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.10,0:04:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得非常的好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.70,0:04:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她继承了巫女的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经过漫长的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.00,0:04:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算走到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.90,0:04:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这其中唯一的错误就是你…克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.60,0:04:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本就不是什么救世主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.50,0:04:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太弱了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.80,0:04:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你实在是太弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.20,0:04:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上会让你知道……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的无能…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.20,0:04:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无能…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.90,0:04:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.30,0:04:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了，克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.70,0:05:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点停止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.10,0:05:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.50,0:05:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你原本就没有任何力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做到这种程度已经很不容易了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.20,0:05:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我劝你还是快点放下肩上的这个重担吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.50,0:05:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.70,0:05:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,职司电光明灭的雷界王-塞基拉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.40,0:05:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自血脉中释放炽烈难当的雷火
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.40,0:05:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴雷击(ThunderBolt)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.00,0:05:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想过去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不会让你们接近克劳德和蕾娜一步的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.30,0:05:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻举妄动绝对会被打成蜂窝的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.70,0:06:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.90,0:06:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样要怎么去救克劳德啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.20,0:06:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了，克劳德还有蕾娜不知道会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.10,0:06:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不要问我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.00,0:06:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气死我了!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.90,0:06:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道我们只有看的份?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.90,0:06:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我们去了也不一定能够帮的上什么忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.80,0:06:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是这样实在太不甘心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣洁的光辉……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『将这道圣洁的光辉导向正轨…』
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.50,0:06:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『就能将恶魔毁灭于无形』
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.90,0:06:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷恩，你有什么发现吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.30,0:06:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那本古书上写的圣洁的光辉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.70,0:06:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是指『拉克尔赫普』吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.10,0:06:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道不是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.10,0:06:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…圣洁的光辉另有所指?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德跟我说过不到最后不要放弃希望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.60,0:06:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只要抱持着一丝希望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.80,0:06:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的圣洁之光……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.90,0:06:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会出现的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.30,0:07:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吧?克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.70,0:07:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要搞清楚，克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.10,0:07:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本就没有资格做救世主
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本就不是我的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.10,0:07:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是卡布力尔制造出来的幻象
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.30,0:07:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.40,0:07:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从你心里复制出来的这个我却比任何人都还要了解你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.80,0:07:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只不过是个无名小卒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德，情势已经不是你可以掌控的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.10,0:08:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个行星再过不久就会毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.40,0:08:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这已经是无可逃避的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.90,0:08:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你根本就不是艾斯贝尔的居民
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以没有义务跟这里的人一起送命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正义、友情、爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.10,0:08:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的想为这些冠晃堂皇的虚名舍弃生命吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.70,0:08:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用舍弃生命也可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.00,0:08:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点停止吧!克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.70,0:08:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你的价值与树根还有石头没什么差别
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.00,0:09:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也不能怪罪到你的身上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.30,0:09:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从来就没有认为自己是救世主…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.00,0:09:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.10,0:09:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很没用…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.60,0:09:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一点我自己比谁都还要清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.80,0:09:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也就是因为这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.70,0:09:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才比任何人都了解大家的痛苦和悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.50,0:09:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…我想要保护他们的心也比任何人都要强
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.90,0:09:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.70,0:09:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火凤破
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.70,0:09:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.50,0:09:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.50,0:10:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到你已经成长到这个地步了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.60,0:10:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…你还没有能打倒我的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.10,0:10:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更不要说拯救这个星球了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.40,0:10:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.50,0:10:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是会战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.60,0:10:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会摇得这么厉害啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.80,0:10:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔石索沙…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.20,0:10:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉西丝，危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.40,0:11:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灭却(Extinction)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.70,0:11:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷恩，你好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.80,0:11:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.70,0:11:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你的真面目吗?卡布力尔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是负责执行卡布力尔大人意志的手下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.90,0:12:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是『魔石索沙』
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.40,0:12:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这趟漫长的旅程就到今天为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.70,0:12:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德，受死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.90,0:12:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.50,0:12:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.20,0:12:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.00,0:12:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.90,0:13:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.40,0:13:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.60,0:13:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.30,0:13:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜…为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.30,0:13:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.40,0:13:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想…保护你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.80,0:13:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我喜欢你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.10,0:13:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.40,0:13:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.30,0:13:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这光芒是……?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.10,0:13:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此请与这圣洁之光一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.00,0:13:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救世主啊…圣洁的战士啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.30,0:14:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此借巫女的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.10,0:14:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秉持圣石之力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.00,0:14:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赐予你光之剑…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿你能以此拯救所有的生灵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.40,0:14:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡布力尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.70,0:14:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会保护大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.40,0:14:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就凭你一个人能做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.90,0:14:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又能够保护得了谁呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.50,0:14:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你休想……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.60,0:14:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷电十字(ThunderCross)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.40,0:14:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀冲击波
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:14:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪亚斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:14:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.80,0:15:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在!克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.20,0:15:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不是一个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.70,0:15:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有很多跟我有着同样信念的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.10,0:15:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好不容易走到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去一直躲在爸爸背影后面的那个我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.30,0:15:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了这些同伴们…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.80,0:15:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去…爸爸对我一直是不可逾越的高墙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.30,0:15:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都会拿我们父子比较
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.90,0:15:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们看到的我只是个大英雄的独生子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.20,0:15:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在这个世界上遇到的同伴却不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.90,0:15:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他们的眼中我只是一个\N叫做克劳德·C·肯尼的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.20,0:16:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了他们才让我重新找回了自我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.20,0:16:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢这些同伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.80,0:16:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要一想起他们的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.80,0:16:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就觉得满腔热血
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.10,0:16:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涌出源源不绝的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.00,0:16:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我才体会到爸爸将雷射枪交给我的用心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.90,0:16:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今我一直认为爸爸是为了无能的我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.30,0:16:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才把他自己的武器交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.20,0:16:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那只是我的误解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.00,0:16:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他希望我能够保护自己最宝贝的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.10,0:16:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是爸爸当初将雷射枪交给我的用意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.40,0:16:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我终于了解到爸爸的用心了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.70,0:16:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用这双手保护我最重要的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.10,0:17:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.50,0:17:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣洁的光辉…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.20,0:17:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错!那就是圣洁的光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.60,0:17:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.50,0:17:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.10,0:17:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.80,0:17:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都相信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.60,0:18:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德，你绝对会赢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.80,0:18:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害，你好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.30,0:18:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德真是太神了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.80,0:18:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得漂亮，克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.00,0:18:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪亚斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.20,0:18:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场战斗还结束呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.40,0:18:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色的月亮…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.50,0:18:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算打倒我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是无法终止我的主人这项伟大的计画
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.50,0:18:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡布力尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.20,0:18:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.70,0:18:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们既然把魔石索沙解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.70,0:18:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色的月亮不就应该消失了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.10,0:18:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就跟这个星球一起灭亡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.60,0:18:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.70,0:18:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.30,0:18:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:18:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉耐?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.60,0:19:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉耐，是你停止了时间之流吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.60,0:19:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.80,0:19:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你魔族之王…也不可能全身而退的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.00,0:19:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命会耗尽的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.30,0:19:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.50,0:19:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类哟…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.10,0:19:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这场充满勇气的战斗…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.40,0:19:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我全部都看在眼里…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.90,0:19:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次轮到我来保护这个星球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.40,0:19:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时作为承认你们的证明…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.00,0:19:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉耐…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是当我的生命耗尽之时\N时间将再次流动…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.80,0:19:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.50,0:19:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会做我该做得事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也去完成该做的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.90,0:19:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧，克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.70,0:19:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了拯救艾斯贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.40,0:19:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不会再有第二第三个艾斯贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.80,0:19:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时空传送装置…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.30,0:19:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该做的事…\N就是利用这个装置去敌人的根据地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.60,0:20:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后切断一切万恶的根源
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.00,0:20:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.90,0:20:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有办法做到吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.00,0:20:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.60,0:20:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我还是要去…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.70,0:20:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在打倒真正的敌人之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.50,0:20:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的旅程不会结束…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.10,0:20:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次你不会一个人去吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.30,0:20:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.40,0:20:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.90,0:20:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.40,0:20:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 出发
